### Useful Resources:

**Maritime Domain:**
- IMO regulations: www.imo.org
- Maritime equipment standards: DNV, ABS, Lloyd's Register
- Weather data: NOAA, met.no, weatherapi.com
- AIS data: Marine Traffic, VesselFinder APIs

**Technology:**
- Claude API: docs.anthropic.com
- Three.js: threejs.org
- React Three Fiber: docs.pmnd.rs/react-three-fiber
- Mapbox: docs.mapbox.com
- TimescaleDB: docs.timescale.com

**Design Inspiration:**
- Maritime control rooms: Maersk operations centers
- AI interfaces: ChatGPT, Perplexity, Claude
- Data visualization: Observable, D3 gallery
- Dashboard design: Grafana, Datadog, Tableau

### Glossary:

- **AHTS**: Anchor Handling Tug Supply vessel
- **PSV**: Platform Supply Vessel
- **ISM Code**: International Safety Management Code
- **SOLAS**: Safety of Life at Sea convention
- **MARPOL**: Marine Pollution prevention
- **AIS**: Automatic Identification System
- **CMMS**: Computerized Maintenance Management System
- **ERP**: Enterprise Resource Planning
- **ESG**: Environmental, Social, Governance
- **MIP**: Mixed Integer Programming
- **LSTM**: Long Short-Term Memory (neural network)

